    MORClassifyConcept, MORDefinitionConcept, MORFullConcept, MORHierarchicalConcept

    public abstract class MORConceptBase
extends MORBase<org.semanticweb.owlapi.model.OWLClass>
implements MORConcept
    The base MORConcept class Descriptor.

    This class is shared between all the Descriptors that uses aMOR. It is just define MORBase for an ConceptInstance to be used for MORConcepts. Please, see those classes for more documentations.
